snippet.title: Second Wave - Early Access Release Date Announcement
snippet.description:
Welcome to the world of Second Wave, where the battle for supremacy is about to begin! Get ready to dive headfirst into a world that combines the best elements of competitive team-based shooters into an exhilarating gaming experience unlike any other!

✨ Wishlist Second Wave on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2337510/Second_Wave/
